    "intro_title": "Mamiviet. THE delivery service for the finest sushi in Munich",
    "intro_text1": "Mamiviet. is the No. 1 sushi delivery service in Munich. With us you can order sushi, ramen or poke of the highest quality online and have it delivered directly to your home. In addition to our specials, we also offer you a healthy alternative to the classic canteen in the office or for a romantic dinner or a cozy get-together with friends.",
