      "welcome_text": "All dishes are prepared with special taste by our chefs with great passion and best quality. Come to our restaurant Mami Viet - SUSHI - Asian Cuisine and you will not only find excellent and culinary food, but also feel an atmosphere that invites you to stay longer. Parking spaces are also available directly in front of the door.",
